_sText:
This is the re-release of my more popular map, surf_elites
also, my first release under the solid surf studio

the map is a LONG linear surf map
most (nearly all) of the combat is within the jail
it is also a really hard map, for people new to surf, and even people who have been surfing for a while

Differences between _v1 and _v2:
better lighting
more secrets

custom textures are packed into the .bsp

Have Fun!

Map by: svbg869
        Stephen. V. B. Gilliland.
